page.title: 10FAUNA
page.content: These are some of the animals found this area:-ants,spiders,woodlice,bees, wasps,flies,bees,butterflies,wasps, moths,dragonflies.Larger animals include badgers,rats,weasels,stoats, ferrets,mice,foxes,deer,rabbits,hares, hedghogs,moles,ferral cats,dormice, voles. These are some of the birds found in this area:-wren,hedge-sparrow,owl, bluetit,goldfinch,woodpecker,wagtail, robin,pheasant,songthrush,jackdaw,jay, raven,chaffinch,willow-warbler,magpie, blackbird,wild-pigeon,sparrow-hawk, skylark,kestrel,heron,starling,pigeon. In the summer the following visitors appear swallows,cuckoos,house-martins and swifts. Cold blooded creatures frogs,newts, slow worms,toads and snakes.
